{"tid":266891,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"戒咗大半年即食麵 感覺好咗好多","createTime":"2017-06-01T23:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T03:19:24.000Z","uid":45255,"like":97,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6667dee666ca23e8325c0676be6af26f91881688","tid":266891,"uid":45255,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T23:02:52.000Z","msg":"上年開始戒食任何杯麵同公仔麵，所有調味粉同油炸麵(伊麵除外)再冇食過落肚<br />\n<br />\n成個腸胃會feel到紮實好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔會好似浪下浪下咁飽飽濟濟<br />\n<br />\n仲有頭髮都比先前密返。調味粉累事唔係講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n奉勸咁多位巴絲，早戒為妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係為自己身體著想。<br />\n<br />\n即食麵如毒藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 調味粉同個油炸麵是但一邊都唔好掂。<br />\n<br />\nPS 依家返工日日都食個蘋果或橙tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80449f06a653526d2c56ba10c89d0b599cb246c6","tid":266891,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T23:06:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ceb5e3b6bddf6e68cb0061ce906e0735a803cc1","tid":266891,"uid":80423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T23:07:27.000Z","msg":"健生"},{"pid":"b82b4a495a9a72f02367788188ed6fd90d08c6a2","tid":266891,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916d8428f0a0231cacd131d91b434679a0bafad0","tid":266891,"uid":48295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:41:20.000Z","msg":"戒左五年 近期狂食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b042d2b8d7b4df15c1008409e3c489b499dd587","tid":266891,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T01:26:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年開始戒食任何杯麵同公仔麵，所有調味粉同油炸麵(伊麵除外)再冇食過落肚<br />\n<br />\n成個腸胃會feel到紮實好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor