quote><br />\n習慣帶生果，自然習慣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實仲有依家早餐都學緊食麥皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca58b1e65e8f524a0e7b5fa01e09e7d4bddb929","tid":266891,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:04:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戒左五年 近期狂食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好喇，無謂功虧一簣"},{"pid":"d5d1b0bf07aa5b9fcfdcbc1e7c3c2d74846ea9e7","tid":266891,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:05:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上年開始戒食任何杯麵同公仔麵，所有調味粉同油炸麵(伊麵除外)再冇食過落肚<br />\n<br />\n成個腸胃會feel到紮實好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔會好似浪下浪下咁飽飽濟濟<br />\n<br />\n仲有頭髮都比先前密返。調味粉累事唔係講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n奉勸咁多位巴絲，早戒為妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係為自己身體著想。<br />\n<br />\n即食麵如毒藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 調味粉同個油炸麵是但一邊都唔好掂。<br />\n<br />\nPS 依家返工日日都食個蘋果或橙tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本仔泡菜仔印印死晒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n長遠慢性自殺嚟。信我。"},{"pid":"d9ce5cd26934a3abc9dabeffc5727814cc826ab2","tid":266891,"uid":68094,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:05:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f71c386e9af40f82d9879372c0c41f21ceb8dffc","tid":266891,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:06:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一次聽日講個腸胃會紮實左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽人講</blockquote><br />\n類似咁樣形容啦，即係冇再漏漏bowbow咁"},{"pid":"26db0e5af46b9059e7dfa8b8679d7a9c5cdd2aa0","tid":266891,"uid":73823,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:06:46.000Z","msg":"戒左即食麵四個月<br />\n戒左凍飲一年三個月 <br />\n感覺真係好好<br />\n但戒唔到雪糕 一個月食兩次左右"},{"pid":"d3b7ff1c027bf3a1a27a75095c531820cd23631d","tid":266891,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:08:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你一樣，完全唔食即食麵<br />\n同時戒酒，戒糖份飲品（包括代糖）<br />\n身體健康左，樣後生左<br />\n扑野可以扑到條女反肚</blockquote><br />\n酒我唔掂，唔識飲<br />\n<br />\n一個月就約三四罐汽水，都知自己飲偏多了"},{"pid":"bf0d3b963f5c2864f46f1c7690986bac06271ff2","tid":266891,"uid":55991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:09:26.000Z","msg":"我食親即食麵後個頭都勁撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又口喝 都唔知係咪d仆街調味粉搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b5a87ac946aec19115e12fc2f72ae65c87010b","tid":266891,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:10:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1b0ba7248f81778b78e796b1c33ad960daad38f","tid":266891,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:11:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb4e44c6975e41793ef4df326b3007db2f28f96f","tid":266891,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:13:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我食親即食麵後個頭都勁撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又口喝 都唔知係咪d仆街調味粉搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n口乾一定會。調味粉作怪。話知係日本進口嘅即食麵。<br />\n<br />\n貪一時香口，苦半日喉嚨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 水龍頭塞口咁灌水飲都解唔到的"},{"pid":"fa0e6d67a279af4e4ae9a498c9a499bc17babfb9","tid":266891,"uid":105773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:15:08.000Z","msg":"我都戒左即食麵同汽水<br />\n不嬲唔中意味精<br />\n食完好口乾<br />\n屋企人食野健康<br />\n唔落太多調味料<br />\n煲湯唔落鹽"},{"pid":"2acc906159c485b99268fb0075b0b16dd11dbef5","tid":266891,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:15:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同你一樣，完全唔食即食麵<br />\n同時戒酒，戒糖份飲品（包括代糖）<br />\n身體健康左，樣後生左<br />\n扑野可以扑到條女反肚</blockquote><br />\n酒我唔掂，唔識飲<br />\n<br />\n一個月就約三四罐汽水，都知自己飲偏多了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n糖份飲品毒害好深<br />\n可口可樂公司用精製果糖，簡直係心血管病的起源</blockquote><br />\n都啱<br />\n<br />\n呢期改緊口飲蜜糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買下維他菊花茶咁"},{"pid":"95fe0a9851385fd6d290c20779943e01074c6bc4","tid":266891,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:15:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d91edb16a6b366cbc2722d7c83715029f9889b6","tid":266891,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:16:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26d343c7d8c7e511d673630ea8a650185a801d89","tid":266891,"uid":17026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:16:41.000Z","msg":"有啲好彩自己以前肥低 <br />\n為左減肥 咩即食麵 凍飲 氣水 個啲都已經無食"},{"pid":"c9ba360d44451a22a2d07b6a9f56fe2db69762de","tid":266891,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:18:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92771e08d1868b8c6e07ca8e0bbaa21f978428ef","tid":266891,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:18:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都戒左即食麵同汽水<br />\n不嬲唔中意味精<br />\n食完好口乾<br />\n屋企人食野健康<br />\n唔落太多調味料<br />\n煲湯唔落鹽</blockquote><br />\n味精要吸收的，人體微量元素嚟。關鍵係咪天然提煉<br />\n<br />\n但係我肯撚定調味粉十成都係化學品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8c78ba41b448fc041586d95d32920b4d2b8ce0","tid":266891,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:21:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同你一樣，完全唔食即食麵<br />\n同時戒酒，戒糖份飲品（包括代糖）<br />\n身體健康左，樣後生左<br />\n扑野可以扑到條女反肚</blockquote><br />\n酒我唔掂，唔識飲<br />\n<br />\n一個月就約三四罐汽水，都知自己飲偏多了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n糖份飲品毒害好深<br />\n可口可樂公司用精製果糖，簡直係心血管病的起源</blockquote><br />\n都啱<br />\n<br />\n呢期改緊口飲蜜糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買下維他菊花茶咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要學習睇標籤<br />\n記憶中維他菊花茶糖份嚇死人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20151116/54432984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20151116%2F54432984&d=Lz%2FlKVMzjY173D09amOymYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c2d7186c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20151116%2F54432984&h=ac589518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20151116/54432984</a><br />\n<br />\n【消委會】菊花茶糖份高 1支維他500ml已近世衞標準</blockquote><br />\n我飲250盒裝，而且都係耐唔耐。通常運完先整盒嚟解下渴咁"},{"pid":"b3439c28f18edb663d172f87fc850bcbefcaeefd","tid":266891,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:22:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a72137e8d65975cd2d79baac3d985d4f958755ff","tid":266891,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲好彩自己以前肥低 <br />\n為左減肥 咩即食麵 凍飲 氣水 個啲都已經無食</blockquote><br />\n加埋運動keep fit, 想唔比女溝死都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf0e666949bfedec8f3eb0a0f79421be872c2eb","tid":266891,"uid":59659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:27:10.000Z","msg":"想快手煮掂一餐有咩代替品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ebdfef45c310ba5b6d16d7f6c7eb84e20e556a","tid":266891,"uid":94541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:28:22.000Z","msg":"好難介,, 自己唔識煮野食 <br />\n唯有加隻蛋落去個面到 好似健康D"},{"pid":"b0175ac4117280b636ef12f619d862cd119ff3e5","tid":266891,"uid":94541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:28:22.000Z"