/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見過鬼怕黑，好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f4cdd6ed85cbb7039ce94ec7a4a4e3516653db","tid":266891,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:34:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73b83e7c692f855f5bdec2e3b867b30ba4a0fbf5","tid":266891,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:34:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想快手煮掂一餐有咩代替品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n煮衛生麵，撈麵可以落蠔油，湯麵自己落少少鹽，油，味精OK</blockquote><br />\n蠔油咪一樣唔健康</blockquote><br />\n前題傾返如何戒掉萬惡嘅即食麵"},{"pid":"e0c1a1365c961b13d8e040bb6a0fb846786261b4","tid":266891,"uid":20455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:37:12.000Z","msg":"壽桃牌嗰啲麵 算唔算係？"},{"pid":"6e5041f40df8a0b3432488074c12e05a0df7ecd9","tid":266891,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想快手煮掂一餐有咩代替品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n素麵／米粉／米線／意粉／烏冬（急凍個種）<br />\n大把麵食非油炸</blockquote><br />\n烏冬我會建議俾貴啲買急凍嘅讚岐。急凍嘅比保鮮嗰啲少好多防腐劑"},{"pid":"6ab39844414154e4bc750b8de179c7f85802a343","tid":266891,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>壽桃牌嗰啲麵 算唔算係？</blockquote><br />\n淨買麵條唔連味粉OK的"},{"pid":"82d65e143354277a69b59a4241bd5541f5e084bc","tid":266891,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:39:33.000Z","msg":"好鐘意食即食麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77d0b5fdb94bb077d5aa4412f731b7dfafaddfb","tid":266891,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>壽桃牌嗰啲麵 算唔算係？</blockquote><br />\n淨買麵條唔連味粉OK的</blockquote><br />\n壽桃牌納含量高到仆街呀 簡直跑嬴大市"},{"pid":"03