073f49496262","tid":266891,"uid":116443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:15:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戒走唔健康嘅嘢感覺正好多，以前最誇張一日3罐汽水宜家一個月都未必有一罐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一年飲半罐 仲要溝水飲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打好徹底"},{"pid":"b5df82a869b84b66b37bca3bc420294e0bb957e4","tid":266891,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:17:28.000Z","msg":"冇錯 好開始<br />\n利申 每年食唔多過2次"},{"pid":"a13fbce848a5bc739a227d73c1dedd8846ea03b0","tid":266891,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:23:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完都想介<br />\n但有無指定野代替品<br />\n<br />\n手打烏冬？</blockquote><br />\n我呢排都開始買烏冬煮，順便落d薯仔紅蘿蔔，想食肉就落d雞胸落去，<br />\n之後落少少超市買返黎既日本都麵汁<br />\n其實幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46bb439f51328867b3f4e1cc45496ffdeb3e75bf","tid":266891,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:40:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"721e57f106d7ad05f2c008b136f6f153ed127d77","tid":266891,"uid":96007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:42:18.000Z","msg":"超市買個啲直身通常唔跟味粉嘅面算唔算<br />\n咩上海面 素面 蕎麥面<br />\n純粹覺得公仔面唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾年了但唔覺身體好或者瘦左"},{"pid":"de5391e81eaa4ce7c59d43ed56d1e9258290294d","tid":266891,"uid":4360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>超市買個啲直身通常唔跟味粉嘅面算唔算<br />\n咩上海面 素面 蕎麥面<br />\n純粹覺得公仔面唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾年了但唔覺身體好或者瘦左</blockquote><br />\n未必淨係關即食面事架<br />\n仲有加工肉類或者味精或者糖份飲品<br />\n生活習慣eg早瞓 瞓得好唔好 飲水份量 都會影響到<br />\n<br />\n有得揀我覺得粉絲 意粉 通粉 全蛋麵會好d"},{"pid":"cb1768f910c5d9bfe8621e533896c262237291bc","tid":266891,"uid":32263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>超市買個啲直身通常唔跟味粉嘅面算唔算<br />\n咩上海面 素面 蕎麥面<br />\n純粹覺得公仔面唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾年了但唔覺身體好或者瘦左</blockquote><br />\n新鮮麵舖既上海麵超好食<br />\n不過麻煩在三五七日就要入貨"},{"pid":"28b2153ebfce7d770974b85209703d66a1f39a3b","tid":266891,"uid":90489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T06:07:45.000Z","msg":"米線，米粉，烏冬呢啲嘢食既Gi值都比較高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食得多會易肥"},{"pid":"48edffa6e9df13da662c65a3510e76ea708c6064","tid":266891,"uid":8539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T06:23:18.000Z","msg":"蕎麥麵加日本麵汁"},{"pid":"43f4d132b7cce36eb43a5226857a876b1df97857","tid":266891,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T06:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>米線，米粉，烏冬呢啲嘢食既Gi值都比較高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食得多會易肥</blockquote><br />\n同出前一丁，辛辣麵個d比呢"},{"pid":"76fc86c0887283f9e89ca05a09211c3d766852de","tid":266891,"uid":90489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T06:27:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>米線，米粉，烏冬呢啲嘢食既Gi值都比較高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食得多會易肥</blockquote><br />\n同出前一丁，辛辣麵個d比呢</blockquote><br />\n咁當然出前一丁呢啲肥啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又會肥又唔健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899c2d3535f81005f8ad5b21c5a47102e584d082","tid":266891,"uid":91267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"戒左即食麵M記可樂一年<br />\n唔覺有咩分別<br />\n係瘦左D 但我本身都好瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b93ef6f7034f2b2b402d097bfc4d03bbeee006","tid":266891,"uid":104554,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T06:48:50.000Z","msg":"俾樓主嚇親<br />\n煮個面定定驚先"},{"pid":"4bdfd54c13ea2152d724963eda8616daa71ab0d7","tid":266891,"uid":35357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:42:22.000Z","msg":"好耐冇食公仔麵杯麵"},{"pid":"a28fa16f29a2f9c026c3e20e779bebfa73d2f85d","tid":266891,"uid":47433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:43:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>超市買個啲直身通常唔跟味粉嘅面算唔算<br />\n咩上海面 素面 蕎麥面<br />\n純粹覺得公仔面唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾年了但唔覺身體好或者瘦左</blockquote><br />\n新鮮麵舖既上海麵超好食<br />\n不過麻煩在三五七日就要入貨</blockquote><br />\n冇味粉跟嘅麵點煮先好食？"},{"pid":"00eadca31bccf71741ccfaace2be9ec4b2716f0e","tid":266891,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用有氣水取代汽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阿信屋有平<br />\n<br />\n自從我老豆飲左，血壓低左<br />\n<br />\n佢直情當水飲"},{"pid":"2f6a075e42f99395bb4a022c69e830481997c502","tid":266891,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T10:14:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次聽日講個腸胃會紮實左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有效管教好個腸胃。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5d67f157baaac1ba1983ad3278a2bb8aac8848","tid":266891,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T10:16:01.000Z","msg":"樓主好忍得口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fbda81dcb31edb3a77920e21d23ebff0dc81b93","tid":266891,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T10:23:52.000Z","msg":"大方向好<br />\n凍飲難介架啦 但即食面可以<br />\n<br />\n同時我會游水 所以飲凍飲ok la<br />\n唔飲凍野 田野，人生會少好多樂趣"},{"pid":"9e932681a8bb1e6f6f1841d8e3221a4b3ea9241b","tid":266891,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次聽日講個腸胃會紮實左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/02/195938_b14ccbe72e1893eaed5bba05f2a791de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F02%2F195938_b14ccbe72e1893eaed5bba05f2a791de.jpg&h=063dc0d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6881ec41987c508fe4a8ecdf1b0bcbb72373d12","tid":266891,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T02:23:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大方向好<br />\n凍飲難介架啦 但即食面可以<br />\n<br />\n同時我會游水 所以飲凍飲ok la<br />\n唔飲凍野 田野，人生會少好多樂趣</blockquote><br />\n同游水有咩關係，你意思做運動?<br />\n今晚歐聯又要諗食乜宵夜"},{"pid":"92bd79cf2b27212fdc8f5a7427e8f36cbff76c34","tid":266891,"uid":48211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T01:05:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你一樣，完全唔食即食麵<br />\n同時戒酒，戒糖份飲品（包括代糖）<br />\n身體健康左，樣後生左<br />\n扑野可以扑到條女反肚</blockquote><br />\n糖份飲品真係零<br />\n飲凍0t都走甜"},{"pid":"29217f91ea63ea07ca47ff5886884e4c9055b89d","tid":266891,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:39:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蕎麥麵加日本麵汁</blockquote><br />\n蕎麥麵同烏冬真係好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e19bc1f8f88ae3caeee630deba7185ee5fdcad","tid":266891,"uid":114616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:41:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用有氣水取代汽水<img src=\"/asset